---
title: "Annihilation"
format: "book"
category: "v"
yearReleased: "2014"
author: "Jeff VanderMeer"
---
First part of a New Weird trilogy, a first-person narrative of exploring an anomalous and apparently alien 'Area X', somewhere in Florida. Later filmed under the same name (q.v.).

The novel is the principal subject of one of the <a href="https://anchor.fm/anarchysf/episodes/Annihilation--Discussions-of-Bodies-Being-Morphed-empmke">anarchySF podcasts</a>.
